5 expenditures of the behavioral health innovation grant program established in
6 this section to the House Committees on Health Care and on Human Services
7 and to the Senate Committee on Health and Welfare. Specifically, the report
8 shall address:
9 (1) the revenue credited to the Mental Health Innovation Special Fund;
