10 * * * Mental Health and Substance Misuse Literacy * * *
11 Sec. 5. 16 V.S.A. § 914 is added to read:
12 § 914. MENTAL HEALTH AND SUBSTANCE MISUSE LITERACY
13 (a) The Agency of Education, in collaboration with the Departments of
14 Health and of Mental Health, shall select a curriculum to increase awareness
15 about mental health and substance misuse challenges facing youth throughout
16 the State. The curriculum shall include age-appropriate information on:
17 (1) the connection and importance of mental health to an individual’s
18 physical health and overall well-being;
19 (2) resources and tools for maintaining mental wellness, including
20 evidence-based practices used to overcome mental health and substance misuse
21 challenges;
